<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Freshman Science Simulation Archive</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="https://ssl.gstatic.com/docs/doclist/images/infinite_drive_2022q4.ico">
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap">
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; font-family: sans-serif; background-color: #121212; color: #f0f0f0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; min-height: 100vh; }
        nav { width: 100%; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 15px 30px; box-sizing: border-box; }
        nav .logo { font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive; color: #ffd700; font-size: 18px; }
        .content { padding-top: 50px; width: 90%; max-width: 1000px; text-align: center; }
        .title { font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive; font-size: 2.5rem; color: #ffd700; }
        .game-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 40px; }
        .game-card { background: #1e1e1e; border: 2px solid #ffd700; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s; }
        .game-card:hover { transform: scale(1.05); background: #252525; }
        .game-card h3 { font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        button#panic { position: fixed; bottom: 10px; left: 10px; background: #444; color: #777; border: none; padding: 5px; cursor: pointer; opacity: 0.3; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
    <div class="logo">SIM-LAB v2.0</div>
    <div>
        <span style="color: #666;">Student ID: 882910</span>
    </div>
</nav>

<div class="content">
    <h1 class="title">Interactive Physics Modules</h1>
    <p>Select a simulation module below to begin your data collection.</p>

    <div class="game-grid">
        <div class="game-card" onclick="window.location.href='games/slope/index.html'">
            <h3>Module: Vector Velocity</h3>
            <p>Analyzing acceleration on a 3D incline.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="game-card" onclick="window.location.href='games/crossy/index.html'">
            <h3>Module: Logic & Timing</h3>
            <p>Testing reaction speed in traffic flow models.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="game-card" onclick="window.location.href='games/ecosystem/index.html'">
            <h3>Module: Ecosystems</h3>
            <p>Simulating aquatic herd behavior.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    document.addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {
        if (e.key === "~") {
            window.location.replace("https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Main_Page");
        }
    });
</script>

</body>
</html>
